y of the Last Supper that included trans and drag performers.For the closing ceremony, the main performance was spearheaded by a so-called Golden Voyager scouring a lifeless, desolate earth.Along his way, the Golden Voyager stumbled across the goddess Nike as well as hoards of acrobatic performers - or followers - who seemingly brought life back to the earth.Paris Olympics closing ceremony: The Golden Voyager performance sparked uproar|BBCIn the UK, BBC commentator Andrew Cotter explained when the performance kicked off: \\\"The Golden Voyager descends to an earth that is now dark and deserted.\", \"from\": 547, \"to\": 1424, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1078, \"end\": 1082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"score\": 0.8945342989550912, \"rank\": 0.11764538143056145, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\"}, {\"begin\": 1276, \"end\": 1278, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999997089976628, \"rank\": 2.686179303850026e-07, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1280, \"end\": 1283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9976102840514325, \"rank\": 0.0023089641884330805, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}, {\"begin\": 1296, \"end\": 1309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Cotter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andrew Cotter\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Cotter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Cotter\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the tournament's opening extravaga