mony\", \"from\": 7833, \"to\": 7868}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics are supposed to be uplifting.\", \"from\": 7870, \"to\": 7912, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympics\", \"from\": 7870, \"to\": 7882}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is not.\\\"\", \"from\": 7913, \"to\": 7926, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And a sixth surmised: \\\"The #Olympics opened by mocking Christianity.\", \"from\": 7928, \"to\": 7996, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7985, \"end\": 7997, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999606590066714, \"rank\": 3.925937528282449e-05, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"And a sixth surmised\", \"from\": 7928, \"to\": 7948}, {\"ngram\": \"The #Olympics\", \"from\": 7951, \"to\": 7964}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It ended with a satanic ritual.\\\"\", \"from\": 7997, \"to\": 8029, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a satanic ritual\", \"from\": 8011, \"to\": 8027}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, there were some who jumped to the ceremony's defence, with one keen to point out: \\\"It's the Nike of Samothrace.\", \"from\": 8031, \"to\": 8151, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ceremony's defence\", \"from\": 8070, \"to\": 8092}, {\"ngram\": \"the Nike\", \"from\": 8128, \"to\": 8136}, {\"ngram\": \"Samothrace\", \"from\": 8140, \"to\": 8150}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's in the Louvre.\", \"from\": 8152, \"to\": 8171, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Louvre\", \"from\": 8160, \"to\": 8170}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's weird to show it like this.\", \"from\": 8172, \"to\": 8204, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Why not as the statue was originally fully formed?\", \"from\": 8205, \"to\": 8255, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the statue\", \"from