ource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"(sic) LATEST\", \"from\": 8567, \"to\": 8579}, {\"ngram\": \"\\ud83d\\udcf8\", \"from\": 8643, \"to\": 8644}, {\"ngram\": \"The criticism\", \"from\": 8681, \"to\": 8694}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympics organisers\", \"from\": 8707, \"to\": 8726}, {\"ngram\": \"an apology\", \"from\": 8734, \"to\": 8744}, {\"ngram\": \"the offence\", \"from\": 8749, \"to\": 8760}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper parody\", \"from\": 8771, \"to\": 8793}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening event\", \"from\": 8801, \"to\": 8818}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Several religious groups openly criticised the display, including the Vatican which said: \\\"The Holy See was saddened by certain scenes at the opening ceremony of the Paris Olympic Games and cannot but join the voices raised in recent days to deplore the offense done to many Christians and believers of other religions.\", \"from\": 8835, \"to\": 9154, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9114, \"end\": 9124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9708759795125309, \"rank\": 0.029640527377216643, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Several religious groups\", \"from\": 8835, \"to\": 8859}, {\"ngram\": \"the display\", \"from\": 8878, \"to\": 8889}, {\"ngram\": \"the Vatican\", \"from\": 8901, \"to\": 8912}, {\"ngram\": \"The Holy See\", \"from\": 8926, \"to\": 8938}, {\"ngram\": \"certain scenes\", \"from\": 8955, \"to\": 8969}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 8973, \"to\": 8993}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympic Games\", \"from\": 8997, \"to\": 9020}, {\"ngram\": \"the voices\", \"from\": 9041, \"to\": 9051}, {\"ngram\": \"recent days\", \"from\": 9062, \"to\": 9073}, {\"ngram\": \"the offense\", \"from\": 9085, \"to\": 9096}, {\"ngram\": \"believers\", \"from\": 9125, \"to\": 9134}, {\"ngram\": \"other religions\", \"from\": 9138, \"to\": 9153}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"At a prestigious event where the whole world comes together to share common values, there should be no allusions ridiculing the religious convictions of many people.\", \"from\": 9156, \"to\": 9322, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a prestigious event\", \"from\": 9160, \"to\": 9179}, {\"ngram\": \"the whole world\", \"from\": 9186, \"to\": 9201}, {\"ngram\": \"common values\", \"from\": 9226, \"to\": 9239}, {\"ngram\": \"no allusions\", \"from\": 9257, \"to\": 9269}, {\"ngram\": \"the religious convictions\", \"from\": 9281, \"to\": 9306}, {\"ngram\": \"many people\", \"from\": 9310, \"to\": 9321}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The freedom of expression, which is clearly not called into question here, is limited by respect for others,\\\" the Vatican added.\", \"from\": 9324, \"to\": 9453, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The freedom\", \"from\": 9325, \"to\": 9336}, {\"ngram\": \"expression\", \"from\": 9340, \"to\": 9350}, {\"ngram\": \"question\", \"from\": 9385, \"to\": 9393}, {\"ngram\": \"respect\", \"from\": 9414, \"to\": 9421}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 9426, \"to\": 9432}, {\"ngram\": \"the Vatican\", \"from\": 9435, \"to\": 9446}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 spokesperson Anne Descamps addressed the backlash soon after, telling the media: \\\"Clearly there was never an intention to show disrespect to any religious group.\", \"from\": 9455, \"to\": 9627, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9459, \"end\": 9469, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999949978, \"rank\": 5.017211098742366e-12, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 9488, \"end\": 9496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the backlash\", \"from\": 9503, \"to\": 9515}, {\"ngram\": \"the media\", \"from\": 9536, \"to\": 9545}, {\"ngram\": \"an intention\", \"from\": 9572, \"to\": 9584}, {\"ngram\": \"any religious group\", \"from\": 9607, \"to\": 9626}]}, {\"sentence\": \"[The opening ceremony] tried to celebrate community tolerance.\", \"from\": 9628, \"to\": 9690, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The opening ceremony\", \"from\": 9629, \"to\": 9649}, {\"ngram\": \"community tolerance\", \"from\": 9670, \"to\": 9689}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We believe this ambition was achieved.\", \"from\": 9692, \"to\": 9731, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this ambition\", \"from\": 9704, \"to\": 9717}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If people have taken any offence we are really sorry.\\\"\", \"from\": 9732, \"to\": 9786, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 9735, \"to\": 9741}, {\"ngram\": \"any offence\", \"from\": 9753, \"to\": 9764}]}]}"